{"tid":581125,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"網名變成真實姓名　Xbox Live 朋友清單疑發生程式錯誤","createTime":"2018-03-05T05:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T07:26:40.000Z","uid":4661,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c824cd13a4923e0e607fa8443ddef0f4ce78cc99","tid":581125,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T05:17:14.000Z","msg":"垃圾Xbox<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n現時包括 PS4、Xbox One、任天堂 Switch 等遊戲機要上網對戰，都要申請有關帳戶，而這個帳戶在各主機連結的玩家社群上亦會用到。不過近日 Xbox 用戶就遭遇一個重大問題：玩家在登記服務時所用的全名，直接在別人的朋友清單上顯示，原本這裡應該只會顯示網名。有網民擔心全名暴露後，會受到在網上結怨的其他玩家玩家的惡作劇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-03-02-18.18.49-768x407.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2018-03-02-18.18.49-768x407.png&h=9a4504bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nReddit 討論區就有玩家「nadiaface」報告了這個關於 Xbox Live 的程式錯誤，這位網民在有一天起床的時候收到朋友通知：「你的全名在網路上被全部中看到了」。當她實際打開 Xbox One 檢查裡面的 Xbox Live 帳戶時，用戶圖案旁邊出現的並非她的網名，而是包含了姓與名的全名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/s01-768x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2Fs01-768x1024.jpg&h=e07d8f87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n及後這位網民查閱 Xbox Live 上的網友清單，發現有為數不少的朋友也表示了全名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/s03-768x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2Fs03-768x1024.jpg&h=34411f40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後她打開帳戶設定中關於個人私隱的項目，發現「與朋友的朋友分享自己的真實名字」項目無故被變成了「許可」。在 Reddit 討論區上她申訴「這樣遊戲平台變成了Facebook」，她說自己並不希望把自己的真名給其他網友知道，所以特別將顯示玩家真實姓名的選項關閉，料不到卻出現今次這個情況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/s02-768x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2Fs02-768x1024.jpg&h=b3e7d403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而在網民「nadiaface」發出帖子後，有不少網民都指自己都中招，在遊戲社群上暴露全名。有一些登記時使用偽名的人，發現自己的姓名欄變成了微軟帳戶或者登記信用卡的名字。有不少人擔心，自己的真實姓名被公開之後，會遭受到在遊戲平台上結怨的不友善網友的報復，例如美國近日流行的假報警惡作劇。<br />\n<br />\n微軟亦收到了有關報告，並在該 Reddit 討論區帖文上發出回應，指會盡快修復這個錯誤，如有進展會另行通知。外國網媒《Kotaku》向微軟查詢時，得到的回覆也是「已正全力排除今次的錯誤」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/03/03/xboxlivefullname/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2Fxboxlivefullname%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=IgqL%2FwC13eT0wiNoPVn7wDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=dff54e0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/03/03/xboxlivefullname/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"8319773759d5132961299cb6894c17cecf2af108","tid":581125,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:17:41.000Z","msg":"難怪呢D咁嚴重既問題都無咩報導出啦<br />\n原來係XBOX<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecee98b37b513a4fa51c675bab4dd9c8eaa3ec20","tid":581125,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:20:35.000Z","msg":"Xbox 又贏"},{"pid":"dee6a00db1447d7303a8f965976f15d536763ac0","tid":581125,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5008bdef173c08e169540d823abbe4884f36e957","tid":581125,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:26:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾ms<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}